<p><cs><col><b>Straining piece</b></col> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>, <cd>a short
piece of timber in a truss, used to maintain the ends of struts or
rafters, and keep them from slipping. See <xex>Illust.</xex> of
<er>Queen-post</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

